            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Samuel.13:1-39",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Samuel%2013%3A1-39%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Rape%20of%20Tamar%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20son%20Absalom%20had%20a%20beautiful%20sister%20named%20Tamar.%20And%20Amnon%2C%20her%20half%20brother%2C%20fell%20desperately%20in%20love%20with%20her.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAmnon%20became%20so%20obsessed%20with%20Tamar%20that%20he%20became%20ill.%20She%20was%20a%20virgin%2C%20and%20Amnon%20thought%20he%20could%20never%20have%20her.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Amnon%20had%20a%20very%20crafty%20friend%26%23x2014%3Bhis%20cousin%20Jonadab.%20He%20was%20the%20son%20of%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20brother%20Shimea.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E13%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EShimeah%3C%2Fem%3E%20(also%20in%2013%3A32)%2C%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Shimea%3B%20compare%201%26%23xA0%3BChr%202%3A13.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20Jonadab%20said%20to%20Amnon%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20the%20trouble%3F%20Why%20should%20the%20son%20of%20a%20king%20look%20so%20dejected%20morning%20after%20morning%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3ESo%20Amnon%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20in%20love%20with%20Tamar%2C%20my%20brother%20Absalom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sister.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWell%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Jonadab%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%26%23x2019%3Bll%20tell%20you%20what%20to%20do.%20Go%20back%20to%20bed%20and%20pretend%20you%20are%20ill.%20When%20your%20father%20comes%20to%20see%20you%2C%20ask%20him%20to%20let%20Tamar%20come%20and%20prepare%20some%20food%20for%20you.%20Tell%20him%20you%26%23x2019%3Bll%20feel%20better%20if%20she%20prepares%20it%20as%20you%20watch%20and%20feeds%20you%20with%20her%20own%20hands.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Amnon%20lay%20down%20and%20pretended%20to%20be%20sick.%20And%20when%20the%20king%20came%20to%20see%20him%2C%20Amnon%20asked%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20let%20my%20sister%20Tamar%20come%20and%20cook%20my%20favorite%20dish%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E13%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ea%20couple%20of%20cakes%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2013%3A8%2C%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20I%20watch.%20Then%20I%20can%20eat%20it%20from%20her%20own%20hands.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20David%20agreed%20and%20sent%20Tamar%20to%20Amnon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house%20to%20prepare%20some%20food%20for%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Tamar%20arrived%20at%20Amnon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house%2C%20she%20went%20to%20the%20place%20where%20he%20was%20lying%20down%20so%20he%20could%20watch%20her%20mix%20some%20dough.%20Then%20she%20baked%20his%20favorite%20dish%20for%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20she%20set%20the%20serving%20tray%20before%20him%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20eat.%20%26%23x201C%3BEveryone%20get%20out%20of%20here%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Amnon%20told%20his%20servants.%20So%20they%20all%20left.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%20to%20Tamar%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20bring%20the%20food%20into%20my%20bedroom%20and%20feed%20it%20to%20me%20here.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20Tamar%20took%20his%20favorite%20dish%20to%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20as%20she%20was%20feeding%20him%2C%20he%20grabbed%20her%20and%20demanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCome%20to%20bed%20with%20me%2C%20my%20darling%20sister.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%20my%20brother!%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20cried.%20%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20foolish!%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20do%20this%20to%20me!%20Such%20wicked%20things%20aren%26%23x2019%3Bt%20done%20in%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EWhere%20could%20I%20go%20in%20my%20shame%3F%20And%20you%20would%20be%20called%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20fools%20in%20Israel.%20Please%2C%20just%20speak%20to%20the%20king%20about%20it%2C%20and%20he%20will%20let%20you%20marry%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_14%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Amnon%20wouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20her%2C%20and%20since%20he%20was%20stronger%20than%20she%20was%2C%20he%20raped%20her.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_15%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20suddenly%20Amnon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20love%20turned%20to%20hate%2C%20and%20he%20hated%20her%20even%20more%20than%20he%20had%20loved%20her.%20%26%23x201C%3BGet%20out%20of%20here!%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20snarled%20at%20her.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_16%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%20no!%26%23x201D%3B%20Tamar%20cried.%20%26%23x201C%3BSending%20me%20away%20now%20is%20worse%20than%20what%20you%26%23x2019%3Bve%20already%20done%20to%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EBut%20Amnon%20wouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20her.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_17%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20shouted%20for%20his%20servant%20and%20demanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThrow%20this%20woman%20out%2C%20and%20lock%20the%20door%20behind%20her!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_18%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20servant%20put%20her%20out%20and%20locked%20the%20door%20behind%20her.%20She%20was%20wearing%20a%20long%2C%20beautiful%20robe%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E13%3A18%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ea%20robe%20with%20sleeves%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Ean%20ornamented%20robe.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20was%20the%20custom%20in%20those%20days%20for%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20virgin%20daughters.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_19%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20now%20Tamar%20tore%20her%20robe%20and%20put%20ashes%20on%20her%20head.%20And%20then%2C%20with%20her%20face%20in%20her%20hands%2C%20she%20went%20away%20crying.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_20%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EHer%20brother%20Absalom%20saw%20her%20and%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIs%20it%20true%20that%20Amnon%20has%20been%20with%20you%3F%20Well%2C%20my%20sister%2C%20keep%20quiet%20for%20now%2C%20since%20he%26%23x2019%3Bs%20your%20brother.%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20worry%20about%20it.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20Tamar%20lived%20as%20a%20desolate%20woman%20in%20her%20brother%20Absalom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_21%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20King%20David%20heard%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20he%20was%20very%20angry.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E13%3A21%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Dead%20Sea%20Scrolls%20and%20Greek%20version%20add%20%3Cem%3EBut%20he%20did%20not%20punish%20his%20son%20Amnon%2C%20because%20he%20loved%20him%2C%20for%20he%20was%20his%20firstborn.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_22%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20though%20Absalom%20never%20spoke%20to%20Amnon%20about%20this%2C%20he%20hated%20Amnon%20deeply%20because%20of%20what%20he%20had%20done%20to%20his%20sister.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_23%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAbsalom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Revenge%20on%20Amnon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20when%20Absalom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sheep%20were%20being%20sheared%20at%20Baal-hazor%20near%20Ephraim%2C%20Absalom%20invited%20all%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20to%20come%20to%20a%20feast.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_24%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20went%20to%20the%20king%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20sheep-shearers%20are%20now%20at%20work.%20Would%20the%20king%20and%20his%20servants%20please%20come%20to%20celebrate%20the%20occasion%20with%20me%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_13_25%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%20my%20son.%20If%20we%20all%20came%2C%20we%20would%20be%20too%20much%20of%20a%20burden%20on%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%20Absalom%20pressed%20him%2C%20but%20the%20king%20would%20not%20come%2C%20though%20he%20gave%20Abs